question: ..... harry would spend HOURS making out with you. On the couch, standing between your legs while you’re sitting on the counter, in front of his friends. Only letting you up when you need to catch your breath or wipe your mouth before he dives right back in. He wouldn’t care who was around you two... it’s says he’s addicted to your lips and the way you taste,,,,  oh my lort.

exactly!!!

like the times his missus would pull away, his lips would just follow hers closely with a little pout and just generally asking for more.
